data.description: Incredible piece of property with vast potential for addition on the oversized lot (20,037 square feet). Other features include fresh new paint through the interior/exterior of home, completely remodeled kitchen (new granite counter tops and cabinets) and bathrooms (new tub sink and vanity), new ceiling fans, new baseboards throughout, new light fixtures throughout,, new water heater, new wood laminate flooring throughout, a cozy fireplace (gas or wood burning) in family room, covered patio in back yard, wrought iron gate in front yard and much more. Bring your buyers.
